a1<-xtabs(formula=~stroke+gender,data=data)
b1<-chisq.test(a1)
## Warning in chisq.test(a1): Chi-squared approximation may be incorrect
a2<-xtabs(formula=~stroke+hypertension,data=data)
b2<-chisq.test(a2)
a3<-xtabs(formula=~stroke+heart_disease,data=data)
b3<-chisq.test(a3)
a4<-xtabs(formula=~stroke+ever_married,data=data)
b4<-chisq.test(a4)
a5<-xtabs(formula=~stroke+work_type,data=data)
b5<-chisq.test(a5)
## Warning in chisq.test(a5): Chi-squared approximation may be incorrect
a6<-xtabs(formula=~stroke+Residence_type,data=data)
b6<-chisq.test(a6)
a7<-xtabs(formula=~stroke+smoking_status,data=data)
b7<-chisq.test(a7)
x_set<-c(b1$p.value,b2$p.value,b3$p.value,b4$p.value,b5$p.value,b6$p.value,b7$p.value)
x_set<-ifelse(x_set<0.05,'denied','accept')
cate_Var<-c('gender','hypertension','heart_disease','ever_married','work_type','Residence_type','smoking_status')
chi<-x_set
df<-data.frame(cate_Var,chi)
df %>% head
##         cate_Var    chi
## 1         gender accept
## 2   hypertension denied
## 3  heart_disease denied
## 4   ever_married denied
## 5      work_type denied
## 6 Residence_type accept
